gpkg : UI interface for Xiange Linux package management system.


to Install

	configure
	make
	make install 
	just same as auto-tools based packages.


Dependence:
	Bash 
	Coreutils
	Tar >= 1.27.1 
	findutils
	gawk
	sed
	grep
	git

